    "en": {
      "title": "Three killed in van collision",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three people died on the spot in an accident that took place on the Wellavaya-Monarakala main road today.",
        "A mother, father and a child who were walking on the road were killed when a plane hit them.",
        "The van that hit the three men went on without stopping and was recovered by the police while it was hidden in Kukuranpola Praset.",
        "The Puthala police said that the identity of the three deceased has not yet been identified and said that the bodies of the three have been kept at the Puthala Hospital."
      ],
